July 18, 2002

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:

FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON

RYDER EMPLOYEES POLITICAL ACTION COMMITTEE

The Federal Election Commission has made available the final audit report on Ryder Employees Political Action Committee. This audit covers the period of January 1, 1999 through December 31, 2000.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street, NW
title: Final Audit Report on Ryder Employees Political Action Committee
